'''北極大學'''（{{lang-en|University of the Arctic}}，UArctic）是一個包含[[北極圈|北極圈]]內大學、學院及其他組織的協作網絡，其目的是提升北極圈內大學的質量。該計劃在[[北極理事會|北極理事會]]的支持下於2001年6月12日發起。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.uarctic.org/singleArticle.aspx?m=75&amid=80 | title=Milestones in UArctic History | publisher=University of the Arctic | accessdate=2012-01-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016084349/http://www.uarctic.org/singleArticle.aspx?m=75&amid=80 | archivedate=2013-10-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.uarctic.org/compactArticles.aspx?m=73 | title=Mission Statement | publisher=University of the Arctic | date=2006-02-15 | accessdate=2012-01-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329044119/http://www.uarctic.org/compactArticles.aspx?m=73 | archivedate=2012-03-29 }}</ref>

==成員==
{{Main|北極大學成員}}
北極大學現有138個成員和5個准會員。會員中有34個位於加拿大，7個來自丹麥（包括格陵蘭島）、9個來自芬蘭、6個來自冰島、17個來自挪威、46個來自俄羅斯、11個來自美國、1個來自英國。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.uarctic.org/memberslist.aspx?m=589 | title=Members List | publisher=University of the Arctic | accessdate=2012-01-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111226111221/http://www.uarctic.org/memberslist.aspx?m=589 | archivedate=2011-12-26 }}</ref>

===資金===
北極大學成員要向上提交資源，一些國家也會向該組織提供資金，不過加拿大政府在2011年將資金額消减了75%。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.uarctic.org/genprl07_LFhJ6.pdf.file | title=Kansainvälinen Arktinen yliopisto juhlii avajaisia 12. kesäkuuta | publisher=University of the Arctic | date=2006-06-06 | format=PDF | language=fi | trans_title=The International University of the Arctic celebrates its launch June 12 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016084435/http://www.uarctic.org/genprl07_LFhJ6.pdf.file | archivedate=2013-10-16 | accessdate=2013-10-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=Feds cut funding to University of the Arctic | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/north/story/2011/10/18/north-uarctic-cuts.html | newspaper=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] | location=Canada | date=2011-10-18 | accessdate=2013-10-16 | archive-date=2013-01-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130110031127/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/north/story/2011/10/18/north-uarctic-cuts.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 成員也需要上交會費。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.uarctic.org/SingleArticle.aspx?m=770&amid=8554 | title=UArctic Membership Fee | publisher=University of the Arctic | accessdate=2012-01-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210091230/http://www.uarctic.org/SingleArticle.aspx?m=770&amid=8554 | archivedate=2012-02-10 }}</ref>

